'''Ekkar Armaments''', also known simply as '''Ekkar Arms''', was a weapons manufacturing company based on [[Coyn]]. They specialized in knives, daggers and combat armor for [[Coynite/Legends|Coynite]] warriors. Ekkar had offices at the [[Elrood Bazaar]].

